text.description:
Restaurants, cafes, and some touristy destinations as well. This is what you'll find in this vlog - all taking place in VIENNA. Vienna is like a bigger, more edgy Munich, and I LOVED it. The vibes were *immaculate* as some would say. It was vibrant, it was fresh, it was progressive, and the architecture was STUNNING. Oh and of course the food was DELICIOUS. Check out the video, and you'll see!
peace N blessings, Jazzy
